1
00:00:00,170 --> 00:00:02,170
That expression is so cute.

2
00:00:02,330 --> 00:00:03,710
It's just not fair.

3
00:00:03,710 --> 00:00:05,080
Huh?

4
00:00:26,380 --> 00:00:28,000
So cute.

5
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:31,040
I already told you.

6
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:33,710
Your ten minutes and my ten minutes
are two different things.

7
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:35,000
Um, about this...

8
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,170
What do you think?

9
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,420
The party invitations.

10
00:00:39,420 --> 00:00:42,080
Didn't I say to use
the same font as last year?

11
00:00:42,250 --> 00:00:43,630
It should be the same.

12
00:00:43,630 --> 00:00:45,460
If I say it's different,
it's different.

13
00:00:45,630 --> 00:00:47,630
There's no way I'm wrong.

14
00:00:47,630 --> 00:00:47,960
Huh?

15
00:00:48,290 --> 00:00:50,330
Don't we have last year's version
in the records room?

16
00:00:50,670 --> 00:00:51,670
Let's go and check.

17
00:00:51,830 --> 00:00:52,830
Yes, sir.

18
00:00:54,670 --> 00:00:57,290
Sami, don't.
He's coming this way.

19
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:00,500
Are you really going to walk out
looking like that?

20
00:01:00,630 --> 00:01:02,880
But there's no time
to fix myself up.

21
00:01:03,290 --> 00:01:04,750
Ah, last year's invitation.

22
00:01:04,830 --> 00:01:06,880
How about I bring it to your office later
for you to confirm?

23
00:01:07,250 --> 00:01:11,000
That way, we can save
your valuable time, sir.

24
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:15,210
You should've told me that
before I came all the way over here.

25
00:01:15,420 --> 00:01:17,580
My apologies.
It just occurred to me.

26
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:19,790
Never mind.
I'm already here.
